With each connected energy provider,  a portion of the energy will be donated to WPR token 
holders at the time of tokenisation as is described in Donation Of Energy 0.9% in kWh. This en-
ergy may be retrieved proportionally to the amount of WPR tokens held and either consumed 
or sold in the marketplace. Tokens not distributed during the token sale will be locked up and 
unable to retrieve energy. The lockup will last 3-4 years. Therefore, locked tokens might partic-
ipate in the energy donation pool only after year 3-4.



