3.6. WPR - The next generation token

WePower is the next stage in token economy evolution. The great majority of tokens currently 
released in the market, tokenize equity or company future cash flows, both of which do not 
have an existing intrinsic value. WePower tokenizes energy, which has a well established mar-
ket and measurable value.

